  "detailed_description": "Sweven is a game from the heart, A game about a bunny finding its way back to mama and papa rabbit. Help us bring the bunny home. Jump over rivers,run through caves, hide in mythical tribal villages. Evade tigers, fight eagles, and ride behemoth fish.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n* Simple controls<br />\r\n* Relaxing music and realistic SFX<br />\r\n* Dark themed graphics with beautiful scenery <br />\r\n* Uses Metal & Vulkan API",
